         <div xml:id="main">
            <head type="incipit">
               <supplied reason="XTF-compatibility">4 November 1884. ¶  ¶ I ¶  ¶ cannot at all express in words ¶  ¶ how highly honoured ¶  ¶ I feel, noble Baron, by the naming of the ¶  ¶ wonderful Parana Cataract ¶ Bové had named a cataract on the Pa...</supplied>
            </head>
            <p rend="number" xml:lang="de">84.11.04</p>
            <p rend="correspondent" xml:lang="de">To Cristoforo<space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>Negri</p>
            <p rend="location" xml:lang="de">Private<space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>hands.</p>
            <space dim="vertical" unit="lines" quantity="1"/>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-size: 12pt; hyphenate: false; text-align: end; "
               xml:lang="de">4/11/84.</p>
            <space dim="vertical" unit="lines" quantity="1"/>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-size: 12pt; hyphenate: false; "
               xml:lang="de">
               <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>In Worten kann ich Ihnen gar nicht ausdrücken, edler Herr Baron, wie hoch geehrt ich mich fühle durch die Bennennung des grossartigen Parana-Cataracts durch den braven und muthigen Capt Bové! Ich habe versucht in dem beigefügten Briefe, welchen ich Sie zu lesen bitte, meinen innigen Dank diesem ausgezeichneten Forscher auszusprechen. Lassen Sie uns hoffen, dass er bald die Italienische Flagge weit längs der<space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>Küste<space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>von Grahams Land durch unerforschtes Meer führen wird!</p>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-size: 12pt; hyphenate: false; "
               xml:lang="de">
               <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>Ich bin auch ganz gerührt, über die gütigen Gefühle, welche Ihre edle Tochter mir bewahrt, und bewundere das Interesse, welches die<space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>junge Baronin für die geographische Wissenschaft und alles Erhabene zeigt. So steht Sie hoch über die meisten Damen, und hat ganz den väterlichen Geist ererbt!</p>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-size: 12pt; hyphenate: false; "
               xml:lang="de">
               <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>Im geographischen Congresse sollte sich dort doch soviel Einfluss geltend machen, dass für Capt. Bove ein paar kleine Ital. Kriegsschiffe zur weiteren Erforschung the Südpol-Länder frei wurden! Welcher<space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>Triumph würde es für die ganze italienische Nation sein.</p>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-size: 12pt; hyphenate: false; "
               xml:lang="de">
               <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>Ich freue mich, dass Sie sich wohl befinden, und hoffe dass Sie ein Chevreul's Alter erreichen werden mit der gleichbleibenden Geistesfrische des<space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>Pariser Professors.</p>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-size: 12pt; hyphenate: false; "
               xml:lang="de">
               <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>Ich danke Ihnen für Ihre sympathetische Nachfrage wegen meiner Gesundheitsstandes. Der Husten ist geringer geworden, aber noch nicht ganz überwunden; da aber jetzt hier der Sommer nun eintritt, werde ich mich wohl mehr erholen; im letzten Winter konnte ich während 4 Monate das Krankenzimmer nicht verlassen.</p>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-size: 12pt; hyphenate: false; "
               xml:lang="de">
               <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>Der ausgezeichnete General-Consul Italiens und seine edle Gemahlin erweisen mir stets die grösste Güte.</p>
            <p rend="valediction"
               style="font-size: 12pt; margin-left: 1.75in; hyphenate: false; "
               xml:lang="de">Mit dankbarer Verehrung der Ihre</p>
            <p rend="valediction"
               style="font-size: 12pt; margin-left: 1.75in; hyphenate: false; "
               xml:lang="de">
               <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>Ferd. von Mueller</p>
            <space dim="vertical" unit="lines" quantity="1"/>
            <space dim="vertical" unit="lines" quantity="1"/>
            <space dim="vertical" unit="lines" quantity="1"/>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-size: 10pt; hyphenate: false; text-align: end; "
               xml:lang="en">4 November 1884.</p>
            <space dim="vertical" unit="lines" quantity="1"/>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-size: 10pt; hyphenate: false; "
               xml:lang="en">
               <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>I<space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>cannot at all express in words<space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>how highly honoured<space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>I feel, noble Baron, by the naming of the<space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>wonderful Parana Cataract<seg rend="FootnoteReference" style="font-size: 8pt; ">
                  <note type="footnote" xml:id="_ftn0" n="1">
                     <p rend="FootnoteText"
                        style="margin-left: 0.3333in; text-indent: -0.3333in; font-size: 9pt; hyphenate: false; "
                        xml:lang="en">
                        <space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>
                        <seg rend="DefaultParagraphFont" style="">
                           <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>Bové had named a c</seg>
                        <seg rend="DefaultParagraphFont" style="">ataract on the Paranà River, upstream of the city of Paranà, Argentina</seg>
                        <seg rend="DefaultParagraphFont" style="">, in M</seg>
                        <seg rend="DefaultParagraphFont" style="">'</seg>
                        <seg rend="DefaultParagraphFont" style="">s honour:</seg>
                        <seg rend="DefaultParagraphFont" style="">
                           <space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>
                        </seg>
                        <seg rend="DefaultParagraphFont" style="">see Bové (1884), pp 949-</seg>
                        <seg rend="DefaultParagraphFont" style="">50:<space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>
                        </seg>
                     </p>
                     <p rend="FootnoteText"
                        style="font-size: 9pt; hyphenate: false; margin-left: 0.4722in; text-indent: 0in; "
                        xml:lang="en">
                        <seg rend="DefaultParagraphFont" style="">Denomina</seg>
                        <seg rend="DefaultParagraphFont" style="">i tale ca</seg>
                        <seg rend="DefaultParagraphFont" style="">d</seg>
                        <seg rend="DefaultParagraphFont" style="">u</seg>
                        <seg rend="DefaultParagraphFont" style="">ta col nome di<space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>
                        </seg>
                        <seg rend="DefaultParagraphFont" style="font-style: italic; ">Cascata Müller</seg>
                        <seg rend="DefaultParagraphFont" style="">. Voglia L</seg>
                        <seg rend="DefaultParagraphFont" style="">'</seg>
                        <seg rend="DefaultParagraphFont" style="">illustre Botanico australian</seg>
                        <seg rend="DefaultParagraphFont" style="">o</seg>
                        <seg rend="DefaultParagraphFont" style="">
                           <space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>accettare que</seg>
                        <seg rend="DefaultParagraphFont" style="">sto segno di riverenza come l</seg>
                        <seg rend="DefaultParagraphFont" style="">'</seg>
                        <seg rend="DefaultParagraphFont" style="">e</seg>
                        <seg rend="DefaultParagraphFont" style="">spressione della gratitudine per gli ef</seg>
                        <seg rend="DefaultParagraphFont" style="">f</seg>
                        <seg rend="DefaultParagraphFont" style="">icacissimi ajuti che egli si degnò prestare alle mie esplorazioni.</seg>
                        <seg rend="DefaultParagraphFont" style="">
                           <space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>
                        </seg>
                        <seg rend="DefaultParagraphFont" style="">La Cascata Müller dista dal Paranà due miglia circa.</seg>
                     </p>
                     <p rend="FootnoteText"
                        style="font-size: 9pt; hyphenate: false; margin-left: 0.4722in; text-indent: 0in; "
                        xml:lang="en">
                        <seg rend="DefaultParagraphFont" style="">[I<space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>
                        </seg>
                        <seg rend="DefaultParagraphFont" style="">gave</seg>
                        <seg rend="DefaultParagraphFont" style="">
                           <space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>that fall<space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>
                        </seg>
                        <seg rend="DefaultParagraphFont" style="">the<space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>
                        </seg>
                        <seg rend="DefaultParagraphFont" style="">n</seg>
                        <seg rend="DefaultParagraphFont" style="">ame<space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>
                        </seg>
                        <seg rend="DefaultParagraphFont" style="font-style: italic; ">M</seg>
                        <seg rend="DefaultParagraphFont" style="font-style: italic; ">ü</seg>
                        <seg rend="DefaultParagraphFont" style="font-style: italic; ">ller Cataract</seg>
                        <seg rend="DefaultParagraphFont" style="">. I desire the illustrious Australian botanist to accept this sign of re</seg>
                        <seg rend="DefaultParagraphFont" style="">spect as the expression of grat</seg>
                        <seg rend="DefaultParagraphFont" style="">itude for the very effective aid he deigned to give my explorations. The Cascata Müller is about two miles from Paranà</seg>
                        <seg rend="DefaultParagraphFont" style="">.</seg>
                        <seg rend="DefaultParagraphFont" style="">]</seg>
                     </p>
                  </note>
               </seg>
               <space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>by the worthy and courageous Captain Bové!<space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>In the enclosed letter, which I ask you to read,<seg rend="FootnoteReference" style="font-size: 8pt; ">
                  <note type="footnote" xml:id="_ftn1" n="2">
                     <p rend="FootnoteText"
                        style="margin-left: 0.3333in; text-indent: -0.3333in; font-size: 9pt; hyphenate: false; "
                        xml:lang="en">
                        <space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>
                        <seg rend="DefaultParagraphFont" style="">
                           <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>Letter not found.</seg>
                     </p>
                  </note>
               </seg>
               <space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>I have tried to express my sincere thanks to this outstanding explorer.<space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>Let us hope that soon he will<space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>take<space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>the Italian flag far along the coast of Grahams Land<seg rend="FootnoteReference" style="font-size: 8pt; ">
                  <note type="footnote" xml:id="_ftn2" n="3">
                     <p rend="FootnoteText"
                        style="margin-left: 0.3333in; text-indent: -0.3333in; font-size: 9pt; hyphenate: false; "
                        xml:lang="en">
                        <space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>
                        <seg rend="DefaultParagraphFont" style="">
                           <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>Antarctica.</seg>
                     </p>
                  </note>
               </seg>
               <space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>through unexplored sea!</p>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-size: 10pt; hyphenate: false; "
               xml:lang="en">
               <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>I am also quite touched by the kind feelings that your noble daughter has for me and I admire the interest<space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>that the young Baroness shows for geographical science and <space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>everything sublime. Thus she stands high above most ladies and<space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>has completely inherited<space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>the paternal intellect!</p>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-size: 10pt; hyphenate: false; "
               xml:lang="en">
               <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>In the Geographical Congress there<space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>as much influence should be exerted that a couple of small Italian warships be free for Captain Bové for further exploration in the South Polar lands! What a triumph it would be for the whole Italian nation.</p>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-size: 10pt; hyphenate: false; "
               xml:lang="en">
               <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>I am pleased that you are well and hope that you will reach Chevreul's age with the constant intellectual vigour of the Parisian professor.<seg rend="FootnoteReference" style="font-size: 8pt; ">
                  <note type="footnote" xml:id="_ftn3" n="4">
                     <p rend="FootnoteText"
                        style="margin-left: 0.3333in; text-indent: -0.3333in; font-size: 9pt; hyphenate: false; "
                        xml:lang="en">
                        <space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>
                        <seg rend="DefaultParagraphFont" style="">
                           <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>The French chemist Michel Chevreul continued active in science until his death in 1889 at the age of 102.</seg>
                     </p>
                  </note>
               </seg>
            </p>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-size: 10pt; hyphenate: false; "
               xml:lang="en">
               <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>I thank you for your sympathetic enquiry after my health. The cough is lessened,<space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>but not yet completely overcome;<space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>however, because the summer is now coming here, I will probably recover more. Last winter I could not leave my sick room for four months.</p>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-size: 10pt; hyphenate: false; "
               xml:lang="en">
               <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>The excellent Italian Consul General<seg rend="FootnoteReference" style="font-size: 8pt; ">
                  <note type="footnote" xml:id="_ftn4" n="5">
                     <p rend="FootnoteText"
                        style="margin-left: 0.3333in; text-indent: -0.3333in; font-size: 9pt; hyphenate: false; "
                        xml:lang="en">
                        <space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>
                        <seg rend="DefaultParagraphFont" style="">
                           <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>
                        </seg>
                        <seg rend="DefaultParagraphFont" style="">Alessandro<space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>
                        </seg>
                        <seg rend="DefaultParagraphFont" style="">de Goyzueta.</seg>
                     </p>
                  </note>
               </seg>
               <space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>and his noble wife always<space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>show me the greatest kindness.</p>
            <space dim="vertical" unit="lines" quantity="1"/>
            <p rend="valediction"
               style="margin-left: 1.75in; font-size: 10pt; hyphenate: false; "
               xml:lang="en">With<space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>grateful respect</p>
            <p rend="valediction"
               style="margin-left: 1.75in; font-size: 10pt; hyphenate: false; "
               xml:lang="en">
               <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>Your</p>
            <p rend="valediction"
               style="margin-left: 1.75in; font-size: 10pt; hyphenate: false; "
               xml:lang="en">
               <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>
               <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>Ferd. von Mueller.</p>
         </div>
      </body>
